00:16:52.260 --> 00:16:54.660
...y desearía su permiso para lanzar al Sound Force.

00:16:54.900 --> 00:16:56.660
Suponía que usted tenía un plan.

00:16:56.660 --> 00:16:56.990
Si...

00:16:57.510 --> 00:16:58.340
¡El Ataque Minmay!

00:17:09.800 --> 00:17:11.000
El Cañón Macross...

00:17:11.110 --> 00:17:12.680
